Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Patience, patience
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:06.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:11.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lets get on with our first presenter please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:14.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:19.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Viking's Kotouge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:21.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone, hello everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No collar person
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:27.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The correct term is collarless shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:29.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I yearn to teach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:33.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To put it this way, all humans are collarless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:36.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Humans all over the world!    \N-Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:38.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's the one thats wrong but i'm annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A collarless person can talk so much! \N -Please continue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:47.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today I bring you an annual project, please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:52.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2021 Prank Review
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:55.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It‘s here \N -That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:57.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's that time of year again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:00:59.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Since 2014,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:01.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was the first \N -Yes it was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:03.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the eight time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:09.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the show's longest running... ongoing project
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:12.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:13.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:15.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I missed my chance to breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:20.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The most frequently performed project in the program \N -Really getting old
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:23.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't you speak without having to take a breath? \N -I was short of breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:29.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, this is the annual project to see who was pranked the most last year
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:34.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And a snow mountain balloon taro competition\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:57.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,2021 Celebrity Ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First at joint 10th...
