Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:43.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Top-ranked for 3 consecutive years, Ogata drops to No. 7 in 2021
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:47.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next three people appeared the same number of times
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:47.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
