Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:57.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai, Tsuda and Nadal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:02:58.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Less than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:14.68,special_Wed_1,,0,0,0,,{\1c&FFFFFF&\3c&0000FF&\4c&0000FF&\frx-270\t(0,120,\frx-360)\pos(979.5,888)\org(975,840)}2020 Prank{\c\4c\3c}「Video recorded in advance for a long-distance meeting」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:02.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me something interesting about when you played soccer? \N -OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:06.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Funny stories from the soccer team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:06.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pre-recorded video
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:09.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just played a video
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:10.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is it? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An interesting story
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The King of 2020 has failed to achieve a winning streak
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:24.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is a 10-time tie for 2nd
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:31.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yamauchi and Kawai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:29.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unexpected
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:33.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bitter citrus fruit…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:42.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first Johnny's finalist since 2014
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:43.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Johnny's, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who can surpass these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:47.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the top of the list is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda with 12 appearences
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:04:00.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, he is awarded the title of King of 2021
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:04.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so it's Oda this time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:08.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The generations go by so quickly \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Komiya is no longer on the list
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now, its time to get down to business \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:16.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda was pranked so many time this year
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So he must be pretty sensitive to the whole thing by now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:23.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, this week we did seven pranks on Oda
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:26.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then we challenged him to tell us what they were
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You also did it, right? \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:33.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for the traffic light after work from Nagoya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:37.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When the American car that should have been in my house drove past me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:44.57,special_Wed_1,,0,0,0,,{\frx-270\t(0,120,\frx-360)\pos(1036.5,902)\org(1035,862)}2015 Prank
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shipped all the way from Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:44.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The staff drove on the expressway to Nagoya \N -Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:46.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's car theft!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed, indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:51.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One day in December...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definitely a tiring week
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:53.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Exhausting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:56.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda is notified of the results
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:03.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You came first in the celebrity prank ranking of 2021
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh? First? \N -First
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:07.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First place? \N -That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was scary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.73,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda's very scary sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:20.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm always questioning if things are pranks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably because i've been messed with too much
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.66,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everything feels like a prank
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so the plan is put into action
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:34.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can Oda determine the 7 pranks performed in a whole week of pranks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think I can probably tell
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:42.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I won't miss the small details
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:44.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've been here too much
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:47.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm too suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:50.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To narrow it down to 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:59.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are often Assistant Directors who rush in from the corridor
Dialogue: 3,0:05:59.01,0:06:02.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have to react "Oh!" even when I've seen it, just do something
Dialogue: 3,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're really everywhere
Dialogue: 3,0:06:05.25,0:06:09.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Arrangements for the extremely sensitive Oda are as follows
Dialogue: 3,0:06:09.25,0:06:11.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Heightened sensitivity
Dialogue: 3,0:06:10.45,0:06:15.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Someone bangs on the wall after shouting occurs at a location shoot
Dialogue: 3,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.66,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Realistic
Dialogue: 3,0:06:16.14,0:06:21.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Koga Ken sings the BGM in a Cafe
Dialogue: 3,0:06:21.96,0:06:25.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The number of followers round a Z-list celebrity is ridiculous
Dialogue: 3,0:06:26.50,0:06:32.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wear a police chief's uniform for one day from the moment of leaving the house
Dialogue: 3,0:06:33.52,0:06:35.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He really became a chief?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:34.10,0:06:38.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The entire meeting staff are over 190cm tall
Dialogue: 3,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's tall!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:39.24,0:06:42.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first appearance of Ado is a fake
Dialogue: 3,0:06:44.10,0:06:47.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wake up without being woken up
Dialogue: 3,0:06:48.12,0:06:50.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last one's like Ikyo's question
Dialogue: 3,0:06:51.63,0:06:58.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For one week, a camera remains close to Oda to shoot the 7 pranks
Dialogue: 3,0:06:58.66,0:07:05.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After one week, he is asked to guess which of the things that happened around him were pranks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.35,special_Wed_1_3,,0,0,0,,{\move(720,591,720,461,0,120)\bord0\shad0)\c&H47E8FC&\clip(516,372,973.5,462)}After one week
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:18.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What hat are you wearing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:20.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much confidence do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have complete confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have a definitive answer in my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are 7 that I am sure of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it was 6 or 8, then it'd be different
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:33.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's seven, and you've arranged for seven, right? \N -Correct
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:38.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have confidence and also feel a little embarrassed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:40.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm serious
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I apologise
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:44.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am really serious
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:45.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you work out the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think i'm good to go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:51.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does he think is the first prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:57.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If this isn't a prank then its a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:04.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Being the Chief of Police of Shinjuku Police Station for a day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:10.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The night before my manager gave us police uniforms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And told us to wear it to work tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:17.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the police chief costume you will wear tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:22.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Put it on before you go out tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:26.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Later you'll be in a taxi prepared by the police station
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:29.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Put it on in the morning, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now way! Aren't I on "Love it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wear this before "Love it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:36.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then switch to the clothes prepared at "Love it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:37.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just wear this uniform for the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:38.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Start when leaving the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right, start when leaving the house\N  -Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:46.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you'll be a police chief for a day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It definitely felt ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She explained to me that it was because I was going to be a police chief for a day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:52.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We had a little argument
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.65,0:08:56.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even the police chief changes into their uniform at the station
Dialogue: 3,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is what I said
Dialogue: 3,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.79,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He talks like my dad
Dialogue: 3,0:08:58.19,0:09:00.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She said: "No, this is the rule for the police chief on their first day"
Dialogue: 3,0:09:00.56,0:09:04.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I genuinely didn't bring my own clothes, the uniform was my clothes for the day
Dialogue: 3,0:09:04.69,0:09:08.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought this is definitely wrong
Dialogue: 3,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't understand it
Dialogue: 3,0:09:12.43,0:09:13.54,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So weird
Dialogue: 3,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Police chief, police chief!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So weird!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:23.51,0:09:25.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So weird!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:25.51,0:09:28.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is killing me
Dialogue: 3,0:09:28.28,0:09:30.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously
Dialogue: 3,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too interesting
Dialogue: 3,0:09:31.74,0:09:35.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I saw it on the news\N-He was really a police chief for a day
Dialogue: 3,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:37.99,0:09:39.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did he really work as a police chief for a day?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously
Dialogue: 3,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a mess
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:47.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was laughed at by everyone when I entered TBS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:52.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,If he came in like that you'd definitely laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this, a drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:02.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Koga Ken was also wearing a uniform for some reason
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:07.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was also Koga Ken's first day as a police chief
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Koga Ken too
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:17.46,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Left the house as a police chief
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Actually turned up wearing it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:27.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Naturally, Koga Ken knows the setup
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What did they tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They just... just gave it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gave it to me yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:43.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd be taking pictures from the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:44.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Constantly asking questions to tell if it's a prank
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where, here?  \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:48.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Couldn't we just shoot and change here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something was definetely wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very perceptive
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:11:00.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I was on a location shoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:05.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was in a room in a big 6-floor apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And in the room next door there was "BANG"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:10.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like someone was saying I was being too loud
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,An impressive one to come up with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not easy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It could happen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:17.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Get get get get get your spirit up
Dialogue: 3,0:11:17.10,0:11:21.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're demoralizing me! \N -That hurts!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:21.41,0:11:25.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm hurt inside, too, asshole, it's your fault!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:26.48,0:11:27.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:27.51,0:11:30.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is pretty real \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 3,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next door?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's someone living there?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Move over there a little
Dialogue: 3,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 3,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey, is someone living there?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:42.49,0:11:45.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't say a word from that point on
Dialogue: 3,0:11:45.99,0:11:47.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay
Dialogue: 3,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way \N-Not good, not good
Dialogue: 3,0:11:50.99,0:11:54.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's a load of subway stations close to here
Dialogue: 3,0:11:54.80,0:12:01.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not only Musashi Kosugi, but also Moto Sumiyoshi
Dialogue: 3,0:11:59.13,0:12:01.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's like "King's Brunch"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:06.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought this is not something you'd usually expect
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:12.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sure i'd scream if it was me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:15.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for the staff to not consider something like this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:15.40,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:19.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are people living next to where we're shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:26.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for the prank I wouldn't have gone there on location
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:32.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So far, Oda has gotten all the questions right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:41.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was working with Misono
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:44.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've collaborated with loads of people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:50.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We discussed the cooperation plan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:56.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the time, she was surrounded by an unnatural number of people
Dialogue: 3,0:12:56.53,0:12:58.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,7-8 people
Dialogue: 3,0:12:57.43,0:12:58.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He realised!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,OK, thank you
Dialogue: 3,0:13:00.10,0:13:03.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you two wait for a moment, please? \N-OK
Dialogue: 3,0:13:02.57,0:13:05.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Poor Misono
Dialogue: 3,0:13:09.93,0:13:14.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It would be weird to see so many
Dialogue: 3,0:13:15.38,0:13:17.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where did {\i1}this{\i0} Misono come from?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:18.48,0:13:23.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy we can collaborate
Dialogue: 3,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes I'm also very touched
Dialogue: 3,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd definitely be able to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:32.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Misono's hair was in two colors
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Was there one person for each color?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This person in charge of this color and another for the other color?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The makeup was setup in such a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why would it be setup like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:42.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With an agent on hand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:46.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then I was introduced to Koga Ken
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:47.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:49.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I said we have to cooperate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd definitely laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I especially like that one part
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:54.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really want to collaborate on it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First on the oil pipe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That song was so good, I was amazed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:02.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd definetly laugh \N  -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is the guy on the end doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:08.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop myself from laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:12.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I tried really hard to hold it in, but I just couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:14.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was just way too many people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:18.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also asked my agent "Isn't this weird?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:22.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She said: "Maybe musicians are all like that"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"EXILE are also like that"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:29.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can use EXILE as a reference for Misono
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that was it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pretty good  \N-Not bad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:36.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was a pre-taping meeting for a show
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just like this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:41.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was about 4 staff members
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:44.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone was gigantic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:46.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's good  \N-Not bad
Dialogue: 3,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it is possible to get them all right \N -Possibly
Dialogue: 3,0:14:49.87,0:14:53.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably about 190CM
Dialogue: 3,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you  \N-Thank  you
Dialogue: 3,0:14:55.44,0:14:59.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's take a picture to finish
Dialogue: 3,0:14:59.97,0:15:01.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He realized at this moment
Dialogue: 3,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll take the picture
Dialogue: 3,0:15:05.51,0:15:07.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll take it  \N-OK
Dialogue: 3,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,OK, let's start with a smile
Dialogue: 3,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Over 190cm!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So stressful!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,OK, cheese!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.67,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I might not realize
Dialogue: 3,0:15:15.83,0:15:16.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,OK, all good
Dialogue: 3,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next an angry face
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very good, very good
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's still possible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:26.98,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of tall people these days \N-Yeah loads
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:28.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope we can make a good show
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:28.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lets cooperate well together
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:35.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So far, Oda has gotten 4 right in a row
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can he achieve the first perfect score?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:38.79,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:59.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A report in a music program
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:02.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ado who sang "Urusei"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:03.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would you realize if you hadn't seen her before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:06.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was Ado's first appearance on that program
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:09.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was the only person who'd met her before the show
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:12.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although she's a bit out of my league
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:13.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I react to things,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's my job to react to things that happen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:20.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I went to the studio to see Ado
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:25.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The recording studio is over there
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:27.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can we go, is it ok to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:28.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's there, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:24.38,0:16:29.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want to see the imposter
Dialogue: 3,0:16:31.52,0:16:39.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The set is a behind the scene's look at Ado's first live appearence on the show
Dialogue: 3,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.91,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's a teenager, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:42.77,0:16:49.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Doing VTR requires me to look around and at the camera
Dialogue: 3,0:16:51.13,0:16:54.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was an impostor, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,How'd he know?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you look at the camera now?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's the first time her face is shown
Dialogue: 3,0:16:56.83,0:16:59.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, really?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So here we go!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:01.30,0:17:04.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda, please start by shouting "Ado!"
Dialogue: 3,0:17:05.82,0:17:09.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Countdown, 5, 4, 3, 2, 1
Dialogue: 3,0:17:10.41,0:17:12.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ado!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:16.62,0:17:19.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a gentle face...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:19.79,0:17:24.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It took a lot of effort to control myself
Dialogue: 3,0:17:21.86,0:17:23.94,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Being gentle is easy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even if i'm shaken inside, I won't show it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That feeling \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:32.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's already a housewife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:38.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whoa, suuuuuper gentle-looking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:37.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who decided on this lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not what I expected at all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I said "Not what I expected at all"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:47.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I didn't say "she's more mature than I expected"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:48.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This sort of thing shouldn't be said
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:54.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ado's age was announced to the public as 19
Dialogue: 3,0:17:54.89,0:17:58.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The fake Ado that Oda was faced with was 47 years old
Dialogue: 3,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.46,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,But she doesn't look 47
Dialogue: 3,0:18:00.66,0:18:03.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fs66\clip(628.5,990,658.5,1068)\t(0,1500,\clip(628.5,990,796.5,1068))}Ha?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a reaction
Dialogue: 3,0:18:03.80,0:18:09.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the other person couldn't hear me i'm sure I would have said a lot
Dialogue: 3,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I would have said "who's the middle-aged woman?"
Dialogue: 3,0:18:11.71,0:18:16.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But even thought it wasn't Ado it'd still be pretty rude
Dialogue: 3,0:18:16.48,0:18:22.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oda's still got two left to get a perfect score
Dialogue: 3,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.76,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Impressive  \N-Impressive, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He can probably can get a perfect score
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:26.96,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Coffee shop BGM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:30.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After work a taxi was arranged for me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:35.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The driver was an African dude
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:39.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I even asked for his name, it was definitely a prank
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is there any more to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:42.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rare
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:50.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The driver was called Masonga and he was from Tanzania
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:47.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1238,253)}It's really rare to see an African dude driving a taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He drove really normally
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:51.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:57.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I asked him his name just to check
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.70,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,How come he took {\i1}that{\i0} taxi on {\i1}that{\i0} day?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This could also happen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:04.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also asked him "Have you been in Japan long?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:10.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He was a good driver, also knew the best routes to take
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:15.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, Oda gives his first incorrect answer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now let's see the true face of Masonga
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:24.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where would you like to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really rare
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:28.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The program staff conducted an investigation based on Oda's description
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:32.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He was very quick to agree to an interview
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:33.49,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hinomaru Transportation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.86,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It does seem like a prank
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:38.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last prank identified by Oda was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:43.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Love it!" graduation prank
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:52.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The new year's live broadcast wasn't discussed with me in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kawashima suddenly made an announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:20:01.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Today, Oda is gradauting from "Love It!" for a role in a morning drama!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hadn't heard anything about this before
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:05.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today he's graduating from "Love It!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh? I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? Really? \N -Seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:09.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:16.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's over, you're starring in "Come Come Everybody"   \N-Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Starting next week, right?  \N-Ah, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't have the morning drama every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And there's also times when you don't appear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:28.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I thought this must be a prank
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For weeks now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:33.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a connection between these shows?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:34.38,0:20:36.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ano's appearence
Dialogue: 3,0:20:36.72,0:20:38.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It seemed possible
Dialogue: 3,0:20:38.79,0:20:41.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It went on for several weeks
Dialogue: 3,0:20:41.53,0:20:45.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the results are shown above
Dialogue: 3,0:20:46.20,0:20:50.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You got 5 correct
Dialogue: 3,0:20:50.83,0:20:54.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's impossible, impossible
Dialogue: 3,0:20:54.50,0:20:57.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't think its possible I got anything wrong, which ones were wrong?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:02.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which one do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm unsure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:08.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, the police chief thing was definitely a prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:09.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Correct
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:11.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Right?  \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ado was a prank  \N-Yeah, a prank
Dialogue: 3,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Be confident
Dialogue: 3,0:21:16.29,0:21:20.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was close! That was close!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The "Love It!" graudation was a prank
Dialogue: 3,0:21:23.83,0:21:25.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 3,0:21:25.53,0:21:28.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,OI!!!!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:28.17,0:21:29.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:26.65,0:21:30.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tragic! The graduation is real!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:30.27,0:21:33.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to suffer a double blow?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:33.92,0:21:38.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The remaining 3 correct answers were then stated
Dialogue: 3,0:21:38.91,0:21:41.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Masonga was real?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,God, I knew I should have asked more questions
Dialogue: 3,0:21:44.87,0:21:49.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We then asked him to see if there was anything else suspicious that could have been a prank
Dialogue: 3,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The ones I just listed were "high suspicion", I also have a few "moderate suspicion"
Dialogue: 3,0:21:55.56,0:22:02.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only the road in front of my house is iced over like a ice skating rink
Dialogue: 3,0:22:02.10,0:22:04.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We don't know anything about that
Dialogue: 3,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.71,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This really can't be done
Dialogue: 3,0:22:04.71,0:22:08.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A man at Kyoto Station wanted me to do a questionnaire
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.04,0:22:12.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He asked me how old I am, I said i'm 43
Dialogue: 3,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Afterwards he said "Thank you"
Dialogue: 3,0:22:14.92,0:22:17.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I wondered if such surveys are still a thing
Dialogue: 3,0:22:17.52,0:22:20.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why just ask someone's age?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.67,0:22:20.05,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed, indeed
Dialogue: 3,0:22:21.09,0:22:24.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Look's like he doesn't have the right answer
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.41,0:22:29.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we revealed the remaining two pranks
Dialogue: 3,0:22:36.11,0:22:40.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Goodbye Sunday Followed by Monday Take a Break on Tuesday{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:22:40.85,0:22:42.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who's heard of this before?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:42.24,0:22:46.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Feedback was basically 0
Dialogue: 3,0:22:46.50,0:22:49.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't hear \N -Didn't hear it
Dialogue: 3,0:22:56.49,0:22:59.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does it ring a bell?  \N -It does
Dialogue: 3,0:22:59.50,0:23:03.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is Koga Ken's "Goodbye Sunday"
Dialogue: 3,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,H-h-h-how, w-what?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:05.13,0:23:07.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What happened? What did you do?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:07.95,0:23:11.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you have a meeting at a cafe during this period? \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 3,0:23:12.51,0:23:17.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The BGM was this song
Dialogue: 3,0:23:15.61,0:23:16.91,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tough!
Dialogue: 3,0:23:19.67,0:23:22.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is the last one
Dialogue: 3,0:23:22.77,0:23:24.89,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The last one is scary
Dialogue: 3,0:23:23.09,0:23:27.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You stayed at Osaka Hotel, right? \N -Right
Dialogue: 3,0:23:27.39,0:23:28.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.96,0:23:32.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah I slept really well
Dialogue: 3,0:23:36.52,0:23:38.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 3,0:23:39.11,0:23:44.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wake up prank without waking up anyone
Dialogue: 3,0:23:44.57,0:23:45.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:45.91,0:23:47.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,W-w-what's going on?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:50.81,0:23:53.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd definitely have this reaction
Dialogue: 3,0:23:53.43,0:23:55.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ijiri didn't know what kind of emotion to feel
Dialogue: 3,0:24:00.62,0:24:02.93,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He really went in but didn't wake him up
Dialogue: 3,0:24:04.06,0:24:06.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not easy for Ijiri to not wake him up
Dialogue: 3,0:24:06.65,0:24:09.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Came in? Came in? Really? \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 3,0:24:09.10,0:24:11.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It must be a lie, right? '\N -No, it happened
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:11.64,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's scary to think about
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:13.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a little scary
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.58,0:24:16.19,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do they look so much alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.48,0:24:19.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's wearing his hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:24.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.87,0:24:28.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He drank it, he drank it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.62,0:24:31.91,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Drinking an unopened one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.02,0:24:35.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Luckily I didn't drink it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.92,0:24:37.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.16,0:24:43.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that he stayed in Oda's room for 10 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:40.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,10 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.79,0:24:43.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's so close
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.69,0:24:45.50,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He didn't realise?  \N -Terrifying
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.09,0:24:51.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\alpha40}Good night
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.73,0:24:56.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For the first time, Ijiri exited the room without waking up the pranked individual
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.72,0:24:58.23,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.23,0:25:00.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ijiri's pranks are all the same
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.61,0:25:02.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really want to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.52,0:25:05.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.19,0:25:08.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's too much \N -OK OK
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.99,0:25:12.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He just got two wrong, what do you think Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.69,0:25:16.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, I thought he'd be able to get them all correct
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.70,0:25:19.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But its impressive he realised the banging on the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.30,0:25:22.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed  \N -It's very like to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.95,0:25:25.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think Matsumura?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.27,0:25:29.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The two incorrect ones did seem a lot like pranks
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.94,0:25:33.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've really never such an African taxi driver
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.92,0:25:37.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was a tense week for him
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.21,0:25:40.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He doubted everything \N -Even ice in front of his door
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.42,0:25:44.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Taking a picture, it's time to take a picture, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.03,0:25:49.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was an unfunny experience for everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.27,0:25:54.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And the fact that the color of his sweatshirt matched the wall behind him was very upsetting
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.07,0:25:56.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unpleasant to look at?  \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.64,0:26:01.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome the next presenter
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.69,0:26:10.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okano Yoichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.00,0:26:10.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.08,0:26:12.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.88,0:26:14.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Your second time here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.35,0:26:18.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was called to come in such a short period of time twice
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.62,0:26:19.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.89,0:26:22.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's a reason for that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.19,0:26:27.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Originally Audrey's Kasuga was supposed to come
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.98,0:26:30.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But he tested positive for COVID-19
