Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.07,0:26:38.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So an immediate search took place for a negative person
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.14,0:26:39.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's me  \N -No, no
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.74,0:26:40.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you a negative person?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.94,0:26:41.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am a negative person
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.91,0:26:43.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are still a lot of negative people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.42,0:26:46.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, there wasn't any negative people available for tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.85,0:26:48.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
