Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.79,0:26:51.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So i'll perform well today also
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.63,0:26:52.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can do it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.32,0:26:55.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Before we get into, please watch this VTR
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.73,0:26:56.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.53,0:27:01.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Balloonist Taro
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.77,0:27:02.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why did he suddenly turn up
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.14,0:27:08.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you do it? That's awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.57,0:27:08.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nostalgic
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.05,0:27:14.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've seen it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.25,0:27:15.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Must admit i've seen it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.81,0:27:17.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This staff member \N -They're all out
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.32,0:27:18.88,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to see this {\i1}again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.52,0:27:20.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please just watch
