Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.00,0:27:40.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What we've just seen is Balloon Taro
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.34,0:27:41.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Balloon Taro
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.53,0:27:43.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you know him Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.17,0:27:45.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've seen him a few times
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.91,0:27:46.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How about you, Niiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.85,0:27:48.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I know him, i've seen him on VTRs
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.89,0:27:49.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh really? \N -That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.81,0:27:55.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today, we bring you a theory related to Balloon Taro, please take a look
