Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.18,0:28:28.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking forward to it at all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.19,0:28:29.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just look forward to it!
