Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.21,0:37:52.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Danger, danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.68,0:37:54.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's going to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.68,0:37:57.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, Kasuga has stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.42,0:37:59.27,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lost his balance?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.27,0:38:00.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even used a drone for this
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.86,0:38:02.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to get up
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.76,0:38:04.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kasgua is standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.93,0:38:08.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The competition is incredibly intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.41,0:38:08.89,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This part is really all about stamina
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.93,0:38:16.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kasuga shakes off the three from the outside and comes to 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.38,0:38:22.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,20 meters from the starting point, Kasuga escapes in a watery melee
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.05,0:38:25.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good, good, good
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.88,0:38:28.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This'll work
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.76,0:38:32.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looks exhausting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.56,0:38:36.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Especiall since its the 2nd stage
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.10,0:38:33.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The back three are still huddled together
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.32,0:38:39.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But Zakoshi and Balloon Taro both suddenly catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.13,0:38:41.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,And this is only the semi-finals
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.28,0:38:42.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.95,0:38:46.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's down
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.55,0:38:49.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does he want to roll? \N-Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.41,0:38:51.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Jun-ichi is a bit far off
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.57,0:38:53.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thigs have reached their limit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.51,0:38:56.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definetly sore
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.54,0:38:58.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Back must hurt too
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.04,0:38:57.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is Jun-ichi losing his strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.26,0:39:02.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Zakoshi enters the final 50m
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.51,0:39:05.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,2nd is Kasuga followed by Balloon Taro
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.08,0:39:07.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Zakoshi's pretty strong
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.05,0:39:14.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Balloon Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.49,0:39:20.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.40,0:39:20.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, he's falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.90,0:39:21.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.94,0:39:24.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very good
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.24,0:39:30.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kasuga actually pushed Balloon Taro off the track
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.23,0:39:26.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.86,0:39:28.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surely this shouldn't be done
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.84,0:39:30.86,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.86,0:39:32.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Halted!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.02,0:39:34.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.56,0:39:37.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The balloon seems to have burst
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.63,0:39:39.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Those branches are dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.07,0:39:40.19,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, watch out, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.69,0:39:41.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah he can't get up
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.55,0:39:45.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.02,0:39:48.73,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.54,0:39:51.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.37,0:39:57.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.16,0:39:59.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kasuga sure is a formidable opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.55,0:39:59.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Trying to grab the tree to get back on the track, he fails
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.92,0:40:02.27,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kasuga's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.00,0:40:05.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Balloon Taro is eliminated
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.53,0:40:07.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's down
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.79,0:40:10.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And Zakoshi is the first to reach the finish line
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.06,0:40:13.64,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Zakoshi has really good stamina
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.64,0:40:15.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Zakoshi's balloon doesn't even leak
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.24,0:40:17.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's only one spot left to advance to the final
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.76,0:40:19.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kasuga is almost at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.04,0:40:24.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, is there a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.66,0:40:24.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Or will Jun-ichi Davidson make a miraculous comeback?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.40,0:40:26.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.41,0:40:28.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.01,0:40:33.10,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.12,0:40:32.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Jun-ichi suddenly self-destructs, throwing himself off the track
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.59,0:40:35.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.91,0:40:42.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kasuga successfully reaches the finish line and advances to the final stage
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.19,0:40:43.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looked pretty easy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.68,0:40:45.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So energetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.62,0:40:46.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What happened with Jun-ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.19,0:40:52.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.30,0:40:55.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a pity
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.61,0:40:56.88,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a shame
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.80,0:40:59.61,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,As expected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.08,0:40:58.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, these are the two participants advancing to the final
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.57,0:41:01.64,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's already night
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.64,0:41:02.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's night
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.04,0:41:07.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.68,0:41:09.19,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It seems to be snowing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.19,0:41:10.00,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finalists
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.64,0:41:04.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Snow Mountain Balloon Taro Competition Final!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.80,0:41:07.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Swooosh——!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.00,0:41:12.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's finally the final
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.42,0:41:18.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The time is 8:00 p.m and the temperature 8 degrees below zero
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.32,0:41:19.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Freezing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.36,0:41:21.46,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,8 degrees below zero
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.93,0:41:24.49,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't the angle a bit too extreme?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.49,0:41:25.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not good, and it's winter
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.65,0:41:26.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The final stage, in extreme cold, is a 70m course
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.39,0:41:30.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.97,0:41:31.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.69,0:41:32.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's practically a cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.78,0:41:34.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really impressive, it looks good
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.70,0:41:33.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And almost all of it is a 30° slope, which makes for a very dangerous course.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.00,0:41:36.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You may not really understand just by watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.37,0:41:40.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But from this angle it just looks like a cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.08,0:41:42.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.44,0:41:49.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Snow Mountain Balloon Taro Competition - who will win become the first champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.51,0:41:53.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is underwear necessary for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.90,0:41:55.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'd be dangerous to not
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.87,0:41:57.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How could that be broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.46,0:42:00.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're at a snow mountain so they are frozen and shrunken \N -Very true
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.70,0:42:02.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Probably can't see it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.27,0:42:08.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Snow Mountain Balloon Taro Competition final is upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.74,0:42:12.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On your mark, get set... \N-How will it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.61,0:42:18.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The race begins
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.72,0:42:22.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will red or green be the winner?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.46,0:42:24.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is bad, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.54,0:42:30.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary, scary
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.65,0:42:36.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This would definitely happen
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.56,0:42:38.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, it burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.30,0:42:44.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.50,0:42:50.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous for the staff too
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.23,0:42:59.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This doesn't have to be Kasuga and Zakoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.73,0:43:04.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Face down
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.12,0:43:05.33,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Terrible, terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.00,0:43:11.80,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,They caught a naked old man
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.93,0:43:13.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.80,0:43:16.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even though it burst \N -Scary, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.81,0:43:19.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who won?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.24,0:43:22.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything! \N -So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.04,0:43:23.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.51,0:43:24.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who won?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.62,0:43:29.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The results were unclear to all
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.40,0:43:32.36,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't see, I can't see Kasuga anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.81,0:43:37.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The winner is, of course, Zakoshi, who reaches the finish line first
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.10,0:43:40.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.76,0:43:42.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The winner of the competition is Zakoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.26,0:43:50.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Swoosh——!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.37,0:43:55.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This game was much more exciting than expected
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.38,0:43:58.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was really fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.28,0:44:01.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the time i'd come back to my senses, it'd already burst
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.65,0:44:04.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really only {\i1}just{\i0} came back to my senses
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.95,0:44:07.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And a bit damp \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.22,0:44:10.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A bit of a Koshino Junko vibe
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.16,0:44:12.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Zakoshi sent the staff flying
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.73,0:44:18.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If he wasn't caught he'd have flown into the building below
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.87,0:44:21.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can't control yourself here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.14,0:44:24.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I tried to brake
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.64,0:44:28.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like I was trying to brake in the car
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.75,0:44:28.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thankfully it didn't burst at the point
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.21,0:44:29.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was very fast
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.58,0:44:32.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After the start I bounced a few times
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.31,0:44:35.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then the ground just disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.52,0:44:37.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bounce bounce bounce then straight down
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.59,0:44:40.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was like falling into a trap
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.32,0:44:45.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After the ground disappeared, my head also dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.66,0:44:47.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The brakes just...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.29,0:44:49.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Slip, slip, slip, slip
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.89,0:44:58.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2810EB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}To sum up\N{\3c\c} The first Snow Mountain Balloon Taro Competition led to 0 injuries
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.34,0:44:58.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone wins
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.97,0:45:00.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very good, very good
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.54,0:45:04.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So what do you think after watching, Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.61,0:45:08.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I apologize for not being interested initially
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.19,0:45:10.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was extremely enjoyable
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.02,0:45:12.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I watched with great interest
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.80,0:45:14.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course, when watching the video it's tough to gauge the speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.61,0:45:18.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In real life it was incredibly fast \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.74,0:45:22.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The fastest thing I've seen this year
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.83,0:45:25.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the scene was it funny to see that sense of speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.67,0:45:29.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I could barely even smile
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.51,0:45:30.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't know whether to laugh or not
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.54,0:45:31.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"So dangerous, so dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.69,0:45:34.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Everyone was shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.09,0:45:36.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the last stage, was it even necessary for people to be involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.65,0:45:38.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed, anyone could have done it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.82,0:45:42.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even a wardrobe would be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.29,0:46:14.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for watching. Support me and get subs early at patreon.com/zwanster03!
